title: LF bronze 3 or higher jg main
body:
i started playing league only this year~ and my game style is quite limited (for now) but im a good player in mid lane i mostly dominate. I like to play around my jg. however it is hard when jg doesn't know what he is doing. need a good or average jg who is more rational. not a lee sin that goes in straight if he gets his q on. it is good if u main 3 or a few champs rather than play random champ each game and feed

my ign shoru097

replies.body: Hey man I just moved to Oceania server from EUW as I've moved to Oz, I know it's not what you're looking for but I'm a Supp main Would you want to run a few normal games to see if we are compatible? Then I'll come back to you for ranked when I'm lvl 30?

Hi I just sent you a friend's request my user name is (ASH IS 1) I play alot of jungle but I can also be flexible and play other lanes as I main a few champions. 

P.S also I am in bronze 4 at the moment reason being I find it boring to play ranked alone or I get matched up with trolls.
